      <title>AT1需求是如此强烈，以至于跳过电话的风险正在上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/at1-demand-is-so-strong-that-risk-of-skipped-calls-is-rising</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最近，对最风险的银行债务类型的需求非常强劲，以至于发行人能够以有利的条件出售证券。德意志银行股份公司只是提醒投资者增加的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/at1-demand-is-so-strong-that-risk-of-skipped-calls-is-rising</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 09:34:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
